<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-3199] Exception field has basic metadata</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3199</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a field of a struct or of an union, or the type of a container is an exception, the metadata associated with the field says it&apos;s a struct, but the value is FieldValueMetaData, not StructMetaData. As a consequence, it is not possible to get the class for the field.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12839999">THRIFT-3199</key>
